WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:04.980
Congratulations to Brother Lin Chuan for his recovery and discharge.

2
00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:08.140
Thank you. Thank you.

3
00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:13.540
I'll take care of you when you get home

4
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.900
My sister has been taking care of you in the hospital recently, and it's been too hard.

5
00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:20.340
Mr. Ye Ji was originally your fiancé

6
00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:22.400
He's okay now.

7
00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:23.720
You just take good care of him

8
00:00:23.720 --> 00:00:25.200
Just adjust your body

9
00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:27.820
It turns out that my sister still remembers that he is my fiancé

10
00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:30.940
Mr. Ji, I will go back today

11
00:00:31.040 --> 00:00:32.740
Elementary school will take good care of you

12
00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:44.520
Look, I really miss you during this time

13
00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:46.500
I've always wanted to go to the hospital to take care of you

14
00:00:46.560 --> 00:00:48.020
But Mrs. Liu wouldn't let it

15
00:00:49.880 --> 00:00:51.340
My mother is also afraid that you will be affected.

16
00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:52.540
I want you to rest.

17
00:00:52.560 --> 00:00:55.720
What can I do to make Mrs. Liu like me?

18
00:00:55.720 --> 00:00:56.900
You don't need to please him.

19
00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:58.900
He will slowly accept it in the future

20
00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:00.660
By the way, Brother Li Shan

21
00:01:00.720 --> 00:01:01.800
I should take my medicine.

22
00:01:01.800 --> 00:01:02.840
You go to rest first

23
00:01:02.840 --> 00:01:04.020
I'll take you to get medicine

24
00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:21.040
Brother Hongchen, you drank the medicine

25
00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:22.420
I'll get you fruit.

26
00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:32.840
Brother, are you not feeling well?

27
00:01:32.840 --> 00:01:34.300
I ask you to go back to your room

